      "id": "60c4a9fd_223baa96",
      "file_path": "Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 32,
      "message": "You can condense all these run commands into:\n```\nRUN mkdir /app/cfg /app/consts /app/api /app/cmd /app/pkg /app/bundles\nCOPY cfg /app/cfg\nCOPY consts /app/consts\nCOPY api /app/api\nCOPY cmd /app/cmd\nCOPY pkg /app/pkg\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7849,
        "name": "Fiete Ostkamp",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de",
        "username": "fostkamp"
      },
      "updated": "2025-02-26 08:16:23.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "c718ba34_d533ed01",
      "file_path": "Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 58,
      "message": "You can combine the two `RUN apt-get` commands into\n```\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y netcat-openbsd curl && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\n\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7849,
        "name": "Fiete Ostkamp",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de",
        "username": "fostkamp"
      },
      "updated": "2025-02-26 08:16:23.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4afcf5ae_e8155c15",
      "file_path": "Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 67,
      "message": "You can combine the `mkdir` commands into\n```\nRUN mkdir /app /opt/policies /opt/data /var/logs\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7849,
        "name": "Fiete Ostkamp",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de",
        "username": "fostkamp"
